title: A Billion Dollar Popcorn Idea
itunes:title: A Billion Dollar Popcorn Idea
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Leisha is looking for a new lucrative popcorn business partner. Kate reveals the ways in which she’s high-maintenance. They then come to the understanding that secret spies probably have it harder than them.
